Here's the annual that I forgot to include:
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7981526/Captain_Britain_and_MI_13_Annual_1(2009)(Minutemen-Dizzy&Tyler)

Ah, nice! This was an excellent series by a great writer, one of those somewhat marginal gems that restore dormant characters to like-ability and proper characterization. Of course, it didn't last, but it was fun.
